    <body>

      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p><rs type="material" key="marmor">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">step</rs>s.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p>Cut on upper face, each next to a gameboard: i. A board,
H.4, deeply cut, (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.13</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.28</measure>). ii. To the west of i, a mill game,
SSS.1 (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.26</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.27</measure>); iii. To the west of this, two concentric squares,
apparently cut for an uncompleted board, type SSS.1 or 2 (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.181</measure> ×<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.186</measure>).</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>i: roughly cut letters, with broad trenches, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03-0.04</measure>; ii, roughly cut,
<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.07</measure>; iii, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03-0.04</measure>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date notAfter="0500" cert="low" notBefore="0301">Fourth to fifth centuries A.D.</date> or later (<rs type="criteria">nomenclature</rs>).</p>
      </div>

      <div type="edition" lang="grc">
        <head lang="en">Edition</head>
        <cb n="i"/>
		  		<ab> <lb n="1"/><persName key="nicetas1" type="aphrodisian" full="yes"><name reg="Νικήτας">Νηκήτας</name></persName> </ab>
			<cb n="ii"/>        
        		<ab><lb n="1"/><persName type="divine" key="Michael" full="yes"><persName key="michael7" type="aphrodisian" full="yes"><name reg="Μιχαήλ"> Μηχαήλ</name></persName></persName> </ab>
			<cb n="iii"/>
				<ab>
	<lb n="1"/> <persName type="aphrodisian" key="zerkounes" full="yes"><name reg="Ζερκούνης"><expan><abbr>Ζερκ</abbr><supplied reason="abbreviation">ού</supplied><abbr>νης</abbr></expan></name><lb n="2"/> <name reg="Μιχαήλ">Μιχαήλ</name></persName> </ab>      
      </div>

      <div type="apparatus">
        <head>Apparatus</head>
        <p>i and ii published as a single text in <bibl n="ALA">ALA</bibl>, without i.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <ab>i: Niketas</ab><ab>ii. Michael</ab><ab>iii. Zerkounes. Michael</ab>
      </div>

      <div type="history" n="locations"><head>Locations</head><p><rs type="found"><rs type="monuList">Temple/Church</rs>; temenos: top step up to south colonnade,
towards east end: .</rs>. Original location: <rs type="origLocation">Findspot.</rs>. <rs type="lastLocation">Findspot.</rs>. </p></div>

      

      

